          "format": "table",
          "rawSql": "-- Tickets dont le statut n'est pas Résolu (5) ni Clos (6)\nSELECT COUNT(*) AS \"Tickets ouverts\"\nFROM glpi_tickets\nWHERE status NOT IN (5, 6)\n  AND is_deleted = 0;",
