          "rawSql": "-- Tickets résolus (status=5) ou clos (status=6) depuis le début du mois\nSELECT COUNT(*) AS \"Résolus\"\nFROM glpi_tickets\nWHERE status IN (5, 6)\n  AND date_creation >= EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM date_trunc('month', NOW()))\n  AND is_deleted = 0;",
